    "title": "Mungu Hufanya Kazi Kupitia Sala",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mungu hufanya kazi kupitia sala",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Mungu ana mamlaka na udhibiti juu ya viumbe vyote. Hata hivyo, anataka watu washiriki wasiwasi wao naye kupitia maombi. Biblia inaonyesha mifano ya Mungu akijibu maombi ya watu. Maombi ni muhimu kwa kuishi maisha ya kumcha Mungu na kutoa huduma bora ya Kikristo. Inasaidia watu kujisalimisha kwa mapenzi ya Mungu.</p><p>Kitabu kifupi cha Nehemia kinasimulia hadithi ya mwanadamu aliyejitolea kwa maombi. Alipoona hali mbaya ya Yerusalemu, Nehemia aliomba kwa bidii kwa miezi minne (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:1\">Nehemia 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:1\">2:1</a>). Maombi yake yalimsifu Mungu kwa nguvu na upendo wake. Nehemia alikiri dhambi za taifa na kumwomba Mungu msaada (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4-Neh1:11\">1:4–11</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:6-Ezra9:15\">Ezra 9:6–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">Danieli 9:4–19</a>). Nehemia alitegemea maombi yake kwa Yerusalemu juu ya &quot;agano la upendo wa Mungu na wale wanaompenda na kushika amri zake&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5\">1:5</a>).</p><p>Waisraeli hawakuwa wamefuata maagizo ya Mungu aliyompa Mose (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:7\">1:7</a>). Kama Mungu alivyokuwa ameonya, kutotii huku kuliwafanya waende uhamishoni. Hata hivyo, Nehemia aliamini kwa dhati kwamba Mungu angerudisha taifa ikiwa watu wangetubu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:8-Neh1:9\">1:8–9</a>; tazama  <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25-Deut4:31\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 4:25–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:1-Deut30:5\">30:1–5</a>).</p><p>Mungu alimpa Nehemia fursa ya kuzungumza na mfalme wa Uajemi kuhusu kurudi Yerusalemu. Nehemia aliomba mwongozo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:4\">Nehemia 2:4</a>). Alitambua kwamba ni Mungu pekee angeweza kubadilisha nia ya mfalme. Baadaye, Nehemia alikabiliana na vitisho dhidi ya wajenzi wa ukuta wa Yerusalemu kwa kuweka walinzi na kuwahimiza watu. Hata hivyo, pia aliomba ulinzi na nguvu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:4-Neh4:5\">Nehemia 4:4–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:9\">9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:14\">14</a>). Alitegemea msaada na baraka za Mungu wakati huo na kwa siku zijazo alipokabiliana na wale waliotenda vibaya.</p><p>Nehemia aliporudi Yerusalemu baada ya ziara fupi Uajemi. Aligundua kuwa baadhi ya Wayahudi hawakuwa wakitoa zaka yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:10-Neh13:12\">Nehemia 13:10–12</a>). Wengine hawakuwa wakishika sabato (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:15-Neh13:16\">13:15–16</a>). Baadhi walikuwa wameoa wasio Wayahudi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:23-Neh13:24\">13:23–24</a>). Alipowakabili kuhusu matendo yao, Nehemia alisali kwa Mungu ili amwonyeshe huruma na akumbuke juhudi zake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:14\">13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:22\">22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:31\">31</a>). Nehemia alielewa kuwa ni nguvu za Mungu pekee zinazoweza kubadilisha watu.</p><p>Yesu alielewa vizuri mapenzi ya Baba, lakini huduma yake ilijengwa juu ya sala (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:16\">Luka 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12-Luke6:16\">6:12–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:18\">9:18</a>). Wakifuata mfano wake, Wakristo wa mapema waliomba mara kwa mara, wakiwa na imani kubwa katika uwezo wake (tazama, kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:36-Acts9:41\">9:36–41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:3-Acts12:11\">12:3–11</a>). Mungu mara nyingi hujibu maombi kwa nguvu. Mungu anataka Wakristo waombe kwa ujasiri, wakitarajia majibu kutoka kwake (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16-Jas5:18\">Yakobo 5:16–18</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:10-Gen24:20\">Mwanzo 24:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:18-Judg15:20\">Waamuzi 15:18–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:6-Ezra9:15\">Ezra 9:6–15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4-Neh1:11\">Nehemia 1:4–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:4-Neh2:5\">2:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:4-Neh4:5\">4:4–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh4:9\">9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1-Ps18:30\">Zaburi 18:1–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:4-Ps22:5\">22:4–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:24\">24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:2-Ps30:3\">30:2–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:22\">31:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:4\">34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:1-Ps40:2\">40:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:7\">81:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:1-Ps106:48\">106:1–48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:6-Ps107:7\">107:6–7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:13-Ps107:14\">13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1\">116:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:5\">118:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">Danieli 9:4–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:1-Jonah2:10\">Yona 2:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24-Acts4:31\">Matendo 4:24–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:16-Jas5:18\">Yakobo 5:16–18</a></p>",
